results.name: Decimal expansion of the density of integers that are divisible by the square of their least prime factor.
program: Pz=primezeta(2); s=0; t=1.; forprime(p=2,1e10, Pz-=1/p^2; s+=t/p^2; t*=1-1/p); s+t*Pz
results.author: _Charles R Greathouse IV_ and _Michel Marcus_, Feb 28 2017
